Starting NPC: Inte Akera (Island 4)<br>
<br>
This quest is slightly unique as it is suggested that you do most of it before speaking to the 'Starting NPC'. I will detail the quest as such<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>1.) Collect Ghoulbane</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Zone: Upper Guk<br>
Who: A Froglok Shin Lord<br>
Objective: Ghoulbane<br>
Level 30 Paladin, LoH<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>2.) Collect Soulfire</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Quest can be found here: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=362">everquest.allakhazam.com/...?quest=362</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>3.) Collect Burnt Book</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Can be looted from Naggy, Talendor, Faydedar, &amp; Severilous.<br>
<br>
Zone: Emerald Jungle<br>
Mob: Severilous<br>
Objective: Burnt Book<br>
Level 60 Shaman, AE Posion of 500+, Chain Stuns, 32K HPs, Need 3-4 groups of 55+<br>
<br>
OR<br>
<br>
Zone: Skyfire Mountains<br>
Mob: Telendor<br>
Objective: Burnt Book<br>
Level 60 Monster, AE 500 on impact, -100hp per tick for 5mins, 32k HPs, 3+ groups of 55+<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>4.) Collect Book of Frost</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Can be looted from Vox, Faydedar, &amp; Gorenaire<br>
<br>
Zone: Dreadlands<br>
Mob: Gorenaire<br>
Objective: Book of Frost<br>
Level 50, AOE Slow, Fear, CHeals, 32k HPs, 3+ groups of 55+<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>5.) Collect Book of Scale</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Zone: North Qeynos<br>
Who: Rineval Talyas<br>
Hand him both books and 1000pp and he will give you the <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Book of Scale</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>6.) Collect Miragul Phylactery</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Zone: Ocean of Tears<br>
Who: Oracle of K'arnon<br>
Give Oracle the Book of Scale and get the Phylactery.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>7.) Collect Miragul Head and Robe</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Zone: Everfrost Peaks<br>
Who: Miragul (undead necromancer)<br>
Objective: Miragul Head and Robe<br>
Level 53, 1500 proc lifetap, double hits for 80-100, 2 groups of 50s<br>
<br>
Have a monk pull 'Lich of Miragul' and then have a necromancer of enchanter CHARM him. Give him the Phylactery and it will spawn Miragul.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>8.) Collect Fiery Avenger</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Zone: Plane of Sky<br>
Who: Inte Akera (Island 4, Pegasus)<br>
<br>
Have one person stay on Island 1 and hand Dirkog Steelhand in the Quest cave 500pp after the Raid part has cleared to Island 4. This will cause Inte Akera to spawn. Hand her Miragul Head, Miragul Robe, Ghoulbane, Soulfire and collect your reward:<br>
<br>
NOTE: Before doing the final turn in go to Erudin and check your faction with the Deepwater Knights. If you are not 'warmly' she will not return the Epic. The actual level of faction required is debatable.<br>
<br>
To raise Deepwater Knight Faction you may do the following quests<br>
